description: This file defines a data model for a movie script using Pydantic, and sets up an agent that utilizes a Cerebras model to generate a JSON summary of a movie script based on location input.

classes.name: MovieScript
classes.description: A Pydantic model representing the structure of a movie script with fields for setting, ending, genre, name, characters, and storyline.

methods.name: print_response
methods.description: Method of the Agent class used to output a response based on input, here invoked with 'New York'.
